# File: app/assets/css/bootstrap-theme.css.ab
# Purpose: Bootstrap 3.3.7 optional theme CSS — unminified copy in app/assets/css/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
Unminified copy of the Bootstrap 3.3.7 optional theme CSS (587 lines). Provides gradient, shadow, and transition enhancements on top of the base Bootstrap grid and components. Development reference counterpart to `bootstrap-theme.min.css`.

## Interface
No exports. Reference file.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file. Requires `bootstrap.css` to be loaded first.

## Implementation Notes
- Bootstrap theme version: 3.3.7
- 587 lines
- Same content as `app/styles/bootstrap-theme.css`
